{"type":"message","id":"c23341f9","parentId":"cda34f29","timestamp":"2026-04-02T17:37:00.451Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:351ea5cd-436c-4963-9a3a-aa4a032243a7 TT Morning Check-In Recap] Good morning Bobby — TT here. Quick recap of where we left off last night:\n\n📋 WHAT WE DISCUSSED:\n- Set up monitoring for @bobby_galletta (TT is logged in and can see your channel)\n- You want to post when you feel like it and see what sticks — organic discovery\n- You're NOT locking into food reactions specifically\n- We talked about cron jobs for your TikTok:\n  • Morning reports (daily stats, new comments, follower changes)\n  • Weekly performance roundup (week-over-week comparisons)\n  • Milestone alerts (smaller ones since you're at 1K followers)\n  • Trend check-ins\n\n❓ WHERE WE LEFT OFF:\nYou liked all those cron job ideas but wanted to talk numbers/details more tomorrow. Specifically:\n- What to include in morning reports\n- What to include in weekly roundups\n- What milestone thresholds to set\n\n💬 REPLY TO THIS and TT will set everything up based on what you decide.\n\nAlso — any new posts since last night?\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 1:36 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-04-02 17:36 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775151420449}}
{"type":"message","id":"e20c70fb","parentId":"c23341f9","timestamp":"2026-04-02T17:37:08.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job message from TT's Morning Check-In Recap. I need to respond to this as TT and ask Bobby about the cron job details so I can set everything up.","thinkingSignature":"b0f8f32f4c97689f47836acc23c2477598509fa906da0a57a7886dad9dbf0c93"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nMorning Bobby! 👋 \n\nI'm ready to set up those cron jobs whenever you give me the green light. Here's what I need from you:\n\n**📊 MORNING REPORTS** — what do you want included?\n- New followers/likes/views since yesterday?\n- New comments (so you can reply)?\n- Top performing post?\n- Anything else?\n\n**📈 WEEKLY ROUNDUP** — week-over-week comparisons:\n- Follower growth %?\n- Total views/likes/comments?\n- Best post of the week?\n- What worked / what didn't?\n- Compare to previous week?\n\n**🎯 MILESTONE ALERTS** — since you're at 1,115, what thresholds?\n- 2K? 5K? 10K?\n- Or maybe engagement milestones too (first 1K views, first 100 comments on a video)?\n- Any dollar milestones once you start making money?\n\nJust reply with what you want and I'll have it all running by end of day. 🔥\n\nAlso — did you post anything new since last night?\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94,"output":266,"cacheRead":10957,"cacheWrite":7113,"totalTokens":18430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775151420450,"responseId":"061ddc3ceca84f010ede1609fe61de5f"}}
